snippet.title: Othello Derby arcade - FULL 1cc
snippet.description: A 1-credit clear of the arcade game Othello Derby [othldrby], played with WolfMAME 0.246. Defeated all five opponents: Monkey, fortune teller, reader, old duffer, and mafia guy.  (The first, second, and third difficulty levels start with the first, second, and third opponents - so starting with monkey is the longest run)
